                     <!-- 
                        1) an enumeration of Christian virtues
                        2) the end of a homily on Sts. Peter and Paul
                        3) A Homily for the Assumption
                        4) an eschatological sermon
                        5) part of an Old Norse translation of the Gospel of Nicodemus (Niðrstigningarsaga)
                        6)  the end of an All Saints’ Day homily
                        7-9) Homilies for Christmas
                        10) The end of a homily dealing with the importance of weeping
                        11) A homily for the Annunciation 
                     (3-4, 7-9: closely related to parts of Maríu saga, could represent a purposeful adaptation
                       of parts of Maríu saga
                       
